The following example shows a style  file  called  book.ist,
 which  defines  an  index  for a book which can be formatted
 independently of the main source:

      preamble
      "\\documentstyle[12pt]{book}
      \\begin{document}
      \\begin{theindex}
      {\\small\n"
      postamble
      "\n\n}
      \\end{theindex}
      \\end{document}\n"


