      \indexentry{alpha}{1}
      \indexentry{alpha!beta}{3}
      \indexentry{alpha!beta!gamma}{10}

 in the input file will be converted to

      \item alpha, 1
         \subitem beta, 3
            \subsubitem gamma, 10

